Super huge lecture hall

Here to take exam
A place where I attended some of the earliest lectures in NTU ... huge lecture hall and those days it was called MLT.
A big lecture theater that can fit up to 1000 occupants, and since it is one of the exam venues for some mid-term exams, it is a fear to some students.
